{
  "name": "面紗法球 Orb of the Veil",
  "type": "equipment",
  "img": "icons/commodities/gems/pearl-purple-dark.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"WordSection1\"><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">這枚由縞瑪瑙製成的球體被懸掛在一根鐵鏈上，球體表面雕刻著螺旋狀的深凹槽。當你攜帶法球時，將獲得如下增益效果：</span><br style=\"WORD-SPACING:0px;ORPHANS:2;WIDOWS:2;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\" /><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">你的感知屬性和感知屬性上限均提升</span><span class=\"1\">2</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\"><br style=\"WORD-SPACING:0px;ORPHANS:2;WIDOWS:2;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\" /></span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">你獲得</span><span class=\"1\">60</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">尺的黑暗視覺，如果你已擁有黑暗視覺，則在原基礎上提升</span><span class=\"1\">60</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">尺。</span><br style=\"WORD-SPACING:0px;ORPHANS:2;WIDOWS:2;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\" /><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">你在尋找暗門和暗道的感知檢定上擁有優勢。</span><br style=\"WORD-SPACING:0px;ORPHANS:2;WIDOWS:2;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\" /><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">詛咒：與這個法球同調的生物將受到其詛咒的影響，只要詛咒還生效，你總會把法球放在觸手可及的地方，不願與它分開。所有非魔法火焰在距離你</span><span class=\"1\">30</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE:10pt;COLOR:black\">尺半徑範圍內自動熄滅，你所造成的火焰傷害減半。</span><br style=\"WORD-SPACING:0px;ORPHANS:2;WIDOWS:2;font-variant-ligatures:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;text-decoration-style:initial;text-decoration-color:initial\" /></p></div>",
